## Security Groups to be created

1. RDS (For connecting postgres)
  - Go to [Security Groups](https://ap-southeast-1.console.aws.amazon.com/vpcconsole/home?region=ap-southeast-1#SecurityGroups) and 
    click on Create new Security Group
  -  Add the following Inbound Rules
| Type           | Protocol     | Port Range        | Source
|---------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Postgres   | TCP   | 5432 | Link serverless security group after creating one in the second step | 
| Postgres   | TCP   | 5432 |

- serverless ( For giving serverless access )
- ec2-rds ( For allowing connections to rds )
- lambda-invoke ( For allowing traffic to invoke lambda inside serverless APIs )
